DatValSQL: SELECT [RecordID] as id,[BMAID] as code,[BrandMarketAllocatorDescription] as description,CreatedDate as createdDate,UpdatedDate as updatedDate,case when Deleted='0' then 'false' else 'true' end as deleted,CreatedBy as createdBy,UpdatedBy as updatedBy FROM [CONATenantData].[v_BrandMarket]

SELECT [RecordID] as id,[EquipmentTypeDesc] as description,[ElementTypeID] as elementTypeId,ISNULL(CAST(ImageURL AS VARCHAR(MAX)), 'null') AS imageURL,CreatedDate as createdDate,UpdatedDate as updatedDate,case when Deleted='0' then 'false' else 'true' end as deleted,CreatedBy as createdBy,UpdatedBy as updatedBy
FROM [CONATenantData].[v_EquipmentType] WHERE Deleted = 0

SELECT [RecordID] as id,[ElementTypeDesc] as description,CreatedDate as createdDate,UpdatedDate as updatedDate,case when Deleted='0' then 'false' else 'true' end as deleted,CreatedBy as createdBy,UpdatedBy as updatedBy FROM [CONATenantData].[v_ElementType];

Select RecordID as id,[FundingTypeCode] as code,[FundingTypeDesc] as description,CreatedDate as createdDate,UpdatedDate as updatedDate,case when Deleted='0' then 'false' else 'true' end as deleted,CreatedBy as createdBy,UpdatedBy as updatedBy from  [CONATenantData].[v_FundingType];

Select [Plan].[v_FundingFreeGoods].RecordID as id
,[Plan].[v_FundingFreeGoods].PlanID as planId
,[Plan].[v_FundingFreeGoods].FundingPackageID as fundingPackageId
,[Plan].[v_FundingFreeGoods].FundingStateID as fundingStateId
,[Plan].[v_FundingFreeGoods].FundingFrequencyID as fundingFrequencyId
,IsNull(Cast([Plan].[v_FundingFreeGoods].CurrentQuantity As varchar(10)), 'null') as currentQuantity 
,IsNull(Cast([Plan].[v_FundingFreeGoods].ApprovalQuantity As varchar(10)), 'null') as approvalQuantity
,IsNull(Cast([Plan].[v_FundingFreeGoods].PlannedQuantity As varchar(10)), 'null') as plannedQuantity
,IsNull(Cast([Plan].[v_FundingFreeGoods].SoldQuantity As varchar(10)), 'null') as soldQuantity
,Convert(nvarchar(255), [Plan].[v_FundingFreeGoods].CreatedDate,126) as createdDate
,Convert(nvarchar(255), [Plan].[v_FundingFreeGoods].UpdatedDate,126) as updatedDate
,case when [Plan].[v_FundingFreeGoods].Deleted='0' then 'false' else 'true' end as deleted
,[Plan].[v_FundingFreeGoods].CreatedBy as createdBy
,[Plan].[v_FundingFreeGoods].UpdatedBy as updatedBy
From [Plan].[v_FundingFreeGoods] Where [v_FundingFreeGoods].PlanID = '101';
